/pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-06/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/mounting-international-sanctions-against-israeli-settler-group-could-be-earth-shattering/00000190-853d-dc2c-a9fa-e57d20fa0000</guid></item><item><title>99 年，奥斯陆协议的制定者为以色列的未来描绘了严峻的愿景。事实证明它非常准确</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-06/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/in-99-ron-pundak-had-a-stark-vision-of-israels-future-it-was-painfully-accurate/00000190-8478-db02-a398-8d7901ad0000</link><description>《奥斯陆协议》的缔造者之一罗恩·庞达克 (Ron Pundak) 在 1999 年对以色列 2025 年的情况做出了噩梦般的预测。今天，在他去世十年后，这一切已经非常接近现实了</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 23:29:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-06/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/in-99-ron-pundak-had-a-stark-vision-of-israels-future-it-was-painfully-accurate/00000190-8478-db02-a398-8d7901ad0000</guid></item><item><title>甚至在哈马斯做出回应之前，内塔尼亚胡就试图破坏人质交易</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-06/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-tried-to-derail-the-hostage-deal-even-before-hamas-responded/00000190-7f58-df13-a798-ffd8b3ad0000</link><description>以色列总理渴望在任何协议中发挥作用，他的同谋贝扎雷尔·斯莫特里奇也有同样的态度。 -法西斯立法</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 21:01:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-06/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-tried-to-derail-the-hostage-deal-even-before-hamas-responded/00000190-7f58-df13-a798-ffd8b3ad0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯在加沙人质协议第一阶段放弃了持久停火的要求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/hamas-informs-hezbollah-it-agrees-to-gaza-cease-fire-deal-netanyahu-gaps-remain/00000190-849d-d161-abd0-cdbddaec0000</link><description>真主党周五还表示，一旦加沙地带休战生效，真主党将停止战斗。然而，以色列总理内塔尼亚胡办公室表示，双方之间“仍然存在分歧”</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 20:58:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/hamas-informs-hezbollah-it-agrees-to-gaza-cease-fire-deal-netanyahu-gaps-remain/00000190-849d-d161-abd0-cdbddaec0000</guid></item><item><title>如何在不影响间谍的情况下处理情报警告：阿什拉夫·马尔万的教训</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/how-to-address-an-intelligence-warning-without-putting-the-spy-at-risk/00000190-83fe-dff5-a5d2-8ffe47540000</link><description>以色列如何能够在不暴露其身份的情况下对情报官员的严重警告做出回应？ 1973 年 10 月的经验教训可能在 50 年后仍然适用</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 19:54:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/how-to-address-an-intelligence-warning-without-putting-the-spy-at-risk/00000190-83fe-dff5-a5d2-8ffe47540000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 273 天：美国官员称哈马斯在停战谈判中做出重大转变</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-273-firefighting-teams-subdue-most-fires-in-north-israel/00000190-83ce-de6b-a9d0-c7cf057c0001</link><description>以色列摩萨德负责人启程前往卡塔尔继续停战谈判 ■ 美国高级官员表示，哈马斯大幅调整立场后，停战谈判取得“突破” ■ 真主党副领导人：目前扩大与以色列的战斗“不可行” ■ 消防队在黎巴嫩猛烈火箭弹袭击后，以色列北部的大部分大火得到扑灭 ■ 战争进入 273 天后，您需要了解以下信息</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 17:01:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-273-firefighting-teams-subdue-most-fires-in-north-israel/00000190-83ce-de6b-a9d0-c7cf057c0001</guid></item><item><title>以色列说服真主党停火的途径取决于与哈马斯达成加沙协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/.premium/israels-path-to-convince-hezbollah-to-hold-its-fire-hinges-on-striking-a-gaza-deal/00000190-8200-d161-abd0-cba90d1c0000</link><description>杀害一名真主党高级指挥官是以色列的一种近乎自动的战术反应，随后来自黎巴嫩的猛烈攻击让人对其效用产生怀疑。 ■ 激进犹太定居者的暴行，包括对安全部队的袭击，令人震惊</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 16:21:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/.premium/israels-path-to-convince-hezbollah-to-hold-its-fire-hinges-on-striking-a-gaza-deal/00000190-8200-d161-abd0-cba90d1c0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦人报告以色列在约旦河西岸杰宁的袭击中造成七人死亡；以色列国防军称其目标是武装分子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-forces-raid-west-banks-jenin-palestinian-medical-sources-report-seven-dead/00000190-82e9-dff5-a5d2-8fe926850000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，巴勒斯坦武装分子被无人机从空中击中，造成杰宁旅特工和一名 54 岁男子在观看屋顶突袭时被狙击手击中身亡。红新月会称另有两人受重伤</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 13:30:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-forces-raid-west-banks-jenin-palestinian-medical-sources-report-seven-dead/00000190-82e9-dff5-a5d2-8fe926850000</guid></item><item><title>全面重新占领加沙并不能保证以色列人的安全。只会煽风点火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/.premium/the-reoccupation-of-gaza-will-not-bring-security-or-deterrence-back-to-israel/00000190-8210-db02-a398-8f1920d10000</link><description>10 月 7 日彻底粉碎了以色列以定居点换取安全的任何想法，并削弱了以色列对其对手的威慑力。无论如何，即使以色列成为加沙地带事实上的管理机构，加沙地带仍将是一个流血的冲突地区</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 11:12:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/.premium/the-reoccupation-of-gaza-will-not-bring-security-or-deterrence-back-to-israel/00000190-8210-db02-a398-8f1920d10000</guid></item><item><title>警方：三名不属于国防军的以色列人涉嫌于 10 月 7 日谋杀一名巴勒斯坦人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/.premium/police-3-israelis-suspected-of-murder-of-palestinian-who-entered-israel-on-oct-7/00000190-81d6-db02-a398-8ddf30a40000</link><description>此案已经调查数月，但法院的禁言令现已解除。这三人涉嫌从阵亡士兵身上夺取武器，并用它们杀死了一名在袭击期间进入以色列的加沙巴勒斯坦人，消息人士称该人持有武器</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 09:09:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/.premium/police-3-israelis-suspected-of-murder-of-palestinian-who-entered-israel-on-oct-7/00000190-81d6-db02-a398-8ddf30a40000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡办公室表示，摩萨德主席从多哈返回后，加沙谈判仍存在“差距”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article-live/idf-soldier-killed-in-gaza-u-s-sees-key-breakthrough-in-hostage-talks-top-official-says/00000190-809b-db02-a398-8d9bb8c20000</link><description>一名男子在以色列北部城市基亚特什莫纳地区被火箭弹击中受轻伤 ■ 法新社：哈马斯官员表示，该组织预计以色列将在周六上午之前对停火“想法”作出回应 ■ 真主党副领导人称扩大与以色列的战斗“是不可能的” “目前这不是一个可行的选择” ■ 真主党领导人纳斯鲁拉会见哈马斯代表团，讨论加沙局势和停火谈判 ■ 巴勒斯坦卫生部表示，在与以色列国防军特种部队交火后，六名巴勒斯坦人在约旦河西岸杰宁丧生</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 02:05:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article-live/idf-soldier-killed-in-gaza-u-s-sees-key-breakthrough-in-hostage-talks-top-official-says/00000190-809b-db02-a398-8d9bb8c20000</guid></item><item><title>为了结束以巴斗争，两个心理现实必须协调一致</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/for-the-israeli-palestinian-struggle-to-end-two-psychological-realities-must-align/00000190-802d-ddc5-a5db-d2ad86600000</link><description>是时候将治疗原则应用于看似永无休止的以色列-巴勒斯坦斗争了吗？</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 00:37:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/for-the-israeli-palestinian-struggle-to-end-two-psychological-realities-must-align/00000190-802d-ddc5-a5db-d2ad86600000</guid></item><item><title>“以色列人要友善得多。在意大利，你可能死在街上，没人会在乎”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-07-05/ty-article/.highlight/people-are-nicer-in-israel-in-italy-you-could-die-in-the-street-and-no-one-would-care/00000190-7ff6-dff5-a5d2-7ff6170d0000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一对以色列和意大利夫妇过着童话般的浪漫生活，还有一位日本侨民，她的孩子们教她变得更像以色列人</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 23:55:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-07-05/ty-article/.highlight/people-are-nicer-in-israel-in-italy-you-could-die-in-the-street-and-no-one-would-care/00000190-7ff6-dff5-a5d2-7ff6170d0000</guid></item><item><title>这位以色列人如何从主要的比比支持者变成主要的反政府抗议者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/how-t